/*NOTE: It's annotated because my school asked for the code from me, and then NEVER USED IT.*/

/*It should be noted that all of these rules have !important at the end to override the original rules, because the way I came up with this is through the use of the Styler Chrome extension, which adds custom stylesheets and scripts to webpages. I still need to override rules, though.*/


/*Import fonts*/

/* latin-ext */
